data.enText: used to show that sth happened or is true although sth else might have happened to prevent it

data.chText: 尽管她竭尽全力控制自己，声音仍然在颤抖。
data.enText: Her voice was shaking despite all her efforts to control it.

data.chText: 尽管他申请了数百个工作，但仍然在失业中。
data.enText: Despite applying for hundreds of jobs, he is still out of work.

data.chText: 尽管她认为物理枯燥无味，她却学得很好。
data.enText: She was good at physics despite the fact that she found it boring.
used to show that sb did not intend to do the thing mentioned

data.chText: 他不想笑，但还是忍不住笑了出来。
data.enText: He had to laugh despite himself.

ex.chText: 尽管丈夫对她不忠，她还是决定要帮他。
ex.enText: She decided to help her husband despite the fact that he had cheated on her.

ex.chText: 虽然他们竭尽全力想赢得比赛，最后还是以4比3的比分被击败。
ex.enText: Despite all their efforts to win the game, they were defeated by 4 to 3.

synonyms.bx: 语气较轻，与 in spite of  相比用得略少。

ex.chText: 尽管下着雨，比赛仍在继续。
ex.enText: In spite of the rain, the game went on.

ex.chText: 虽然丈夫没有自己赚钱多，她仍然爱着他。
ex.enText: She loved her husband in spite of the fact that he earned less money than her.

synonyms.bx: 语气较强，比 despite 更常见。

example: she wanted neither favor nor despite

tr: lack of respect accompanied by a feeling of intense dislike
example: the despite in which outsiders were held is legendary

value.def: You use despite to introduce a fact which makes the other part of the sentence surprising.

example.ex: Despite a thorough investigation, no trace of Dr Southwell has been found...
example.tran: 尽管进行了彻底的调查，还是没有发现索思韦尔博士的任何踪迹。

example.ex: The National Health Service has visibly deteriorated, despite increased spending...
example.tran: 尽管支出在增加，但国民医疗保健服务的质量却明显下降了。

example.ex: He was obviously distressed despite being unconscious...
example.tran: 虽然他自己未发觉，但他显然很忧心。

example.ex: She will stand by husband, despite reports that he sent another woman love notes.
example.tran: 尽管有报道说她丈夫曾给另一个女人写求爱信，但她还是会支持他。

value.def: If you do something despite yourself you do it although you did not really intend or expect to.

example.ex: Despite myself, Harry's remarks had caused me to stop and reflect.
example.tran: 哈里的话让我不由自主地停下来细想。
